long_desc.thetext:
Other qx.ui.menu.Menu may also be affected.

This is zIndex issue. I can workaround it by

      var parentElement = menuButton.getMenu().getContainerElement().getParent();
      parentElement.setStyle("zIndex", parseInt(parentElement.getStyle("zIndex")) + 1);

then menu appears but then all other widgets are blocked. Maybe because there're two instances of qx.html.Root at AUT iframe, maybe because of another reason.
